        <div class="faq-a"><p style="color:#555555;font-size:.88rem;line-height:1.7;padding-top:.5rem">Architectural (dimensional) shingles are thicker, more durable, and offer better wind resistance (up to 130 mph) compared to basic 3-tab shingles. They also have a more dimensional, textured appearance and come with longer manufacturer warranties. Happy Roof recommends architectural shingles for all Florida homes due to our severe weather conditions.</p></div>
